@page "/privacypolicy"
@rendermode InteractiveServer
@inject NavigationManager NavigationManager

<h3>Privacy Policy</h3>

<p>
    Fitness Saviour collects user information to enhance your experience. We prioritise data security and do not share personal information with third parties without consent.
</p>

<h4>Data Collected</h4>
<ul>
    <li>Account information such as username and encrypted contact details</li>
    <li>User-selected preferences (e.g. fitness goals, dietary requirements, accessibility settings)</li>
    <li>Progress data including logged food intake, exercise activity, and weight tracking</li>
    <li>No unnecessary personal data is collected; all data fields serve a clear functional purpose</li>
</ul>

<h4>How Data Is Used</h4>
<ul>
    <li>Generate personalised diet and exercise recommendations</li>
    <li>Customise the user interface to improve accessibility and usability</li>
    <li>Display progress through graphs and summaries</li>
    <li>Improve the accuracy of algorithmic recommendations</li>
    <li>Data is not used for advertising or shared with third parties without consent</li>
</ul>

<h4>Data Storage and Security</h4>
<ul>
    <li>Sensitive information such as passwords and contact details is stored in encrypted or hashed form</li>
    <li>User data is stored securely in a structured database</li>
    <li>Access to data is restricted to authorised system components only</li>
    <li>Security measures are in place to reduce the risk of unauthorised access or data misuse</li>
</ul>

<h4>User Control and Consent</h4>
<ul>
    <li>Users are informed about how their data is used before submitting questionnaires</li>
    <li>Personalisation features are optional and can be disabled</li>
    <li>Users may choose not to provide certain data, though this may limit some functionality</li>
    <li>These practices support data minimisation and informed consent principles</li>
</ul>

<h4>Cookies and Tracking</h4>
<ul>
    <li>Fitness Saviour does not use third-party tracking cookies</li>
    <li>Any session data used is strictly required for system functionality, such as maintaining login state</li>
</ul>

<h4>Policy Updates</h4>
<ul>
    <li>This privacy policy may be updated if system functionality changes; users will be informed of any significant updates</li>
</ul>

<p>
    By using our services, you agree to our data collection practices as outlined in this policy. For more details, please contact us.
</p>

